```plantuml
@startuml michaelsrichter_azure.owasp

actor User
participant Browser
participant "Azure AD" as AzureAD
participant "Insecure Web App" as InsecureApp
participant "ModSecurity WAF" as WAF
participant "Secure Web App" as SecureApp
participant "Azure Resources" as AzureResources
participant "ARM Templates" as ARMTemplates
participant "PowerShell Scripts" as PSScripts

User -> Browser: Accesses Web Application
Browser -> WAF: HTTP Request
WAF -> InsecureApp: Filtered Request (if allowed)
InsecureApp -> WAF: HTTP Response
WAF -> Browser: Filtered Response (if allowed)

alt Authentication Required
    Browser -> AzureAD: Redirect for Auth
    AzureAD -> Browser: Authentication Token
    Browser -> SecureApp: Request with Token
    SecureApp -> AzureAD: Validate Token
    AzureAD -> SecureApp: Validation Response
    SecureApp -> Browser: Secure Content
end

group Deployment Process
    User -> PSScripts: Execute Deployment Script
    PSScripts -> ARMTemplates: Load Template
    ARMTemplates -> AzureResources: Provision Resources
    AzureResources --> ARMTemplates: Deployment Status
    ARMTemplates --> PSScripts: Completion Status
    PSScripts --> User: Deployment Result
end

group WAF Performance Monitoring
    WAF -> AzureResources: Log Security Events
    AzureResources --> WAF: Performance Metrics
    WAF -> AzureResources: Adjust Rules (if needed)
end

@enduml
```